Date: Mon, 13 Jul 2026 23:58:31 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 4/4] Route Gecko pointer streams natively

A mouse once knocked on a DOM-shaped door,
now widgets answer from the proper floor.
Clicks, wheels, cursors, and links stay true,
each tab keeps only what belongs to you.
